metadata.dc:title: Capacidad depredadora de Poecilia (Lebistes) reticulata Peters, 1895 (Cyprinodontiformes: Poecillidae) sobre larvas de Culex quinquefasciatus Say, 1823 y Aedes aegypti Linneo, 1762 (Diptera: Culicidae) en condiciones de laboratorio en Cuba.

[Predatory capacity of Poecilia (Lebistes) reticulata Peters, 1895 (Cyprinodontiformes: Poecillidae) against larvae of Culex quinquefasciatus Say, 1823 and Aedes aegypti Linnaeus, 1762 (Diptera: Culicidae) under laboratory conditions in Cuba].
